title: Universe Sandbox 2 Update 20.3.1
description: Universe Sandbox  is a physics-based space simulator that allows you to create, destroy, and interact on an unimaginable scale.It merges real-time gravity, climate, collision, and material interactions to reveal the beauty of our universe and the fragility of our planet. Universe Sandbox  is the long-awaited sequel to the original Universe Sandbox.Universe Sandbox  includes the desktop version and a VR mode with support for the HTC Vive & Oculus Rift+Touch.
